
- everything you do is trust  
- every vessel is its own trust  
- you tokenize your own trust  
- you protect your own trust  
- no one else defines your value, identity, or authority  

This will be written in a way that is:

- clean  
- ceremonial  
- vessel‑separated  
- safe for public posting  
